#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic Functions"
msgstr "Osnovne funkcije"

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Controls"
msgstr "Kontrolniki"

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a rather short but important section that will go into the details "
"of controlling &krusader;. This section does not try to cover all the "
"various key combinations for two reasons: <orderedlist numeration=\"arabic"
"\"> <listitem> <para>there are just too many of them</para> </listitem> "
"<listitem> <para>most of &krusader; actions are configurable in the <link "
"linkend=\"konfig-panel\">Konfigurator Panel page</link></para> </listitem> </"
"orderedlist>We will only mention the most important keyboard shortcuts with "
"the default configuration, but keep in mind that most of the <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Key-Bindings</link> are configurable. If you find that you "
"use a certain command a lot and want to know the shortcut for this command, "
"or you want to change this command shortcut, then check out the <link "
"linkend=\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"To je precej kratek, a pomemben razdelek, ki bo obravnaval podrobnosti "
"nadzora &krusader;. Ta razdelek ne poskuša zajeti vseh različnih kombinacij "
"tipk iz dveh razlogov: <orderedlist numeration=\"arabic\"> <listitem> "
"<para>preprosto jih je preveč</para> </listitem> <listitem> <para >večina "
"&krusader; dejanja je mogoče konfigurirati na <link linkend=\"konfig-panel"
"\">strani plošče konfiguratorja</link></para> </listitem> </"
"orderedlist>Omenili bomo samo najpomembnejše bližnjice na tipkovnici s "
"privzeto konfiguracijo, vendar ohranimo ne pozabite, da je večino <link "
"linkend=\"key_bindings\">Key-Bindings</link> mogoče konfigurirati. Če "
"ugotovite, da pogosto uporabljate določen ukaz in želite izvedeti bližnjico "
"za ta ukaz ali želite spremeniti to ukazno bližnjico, si oglejte okno <link "
"linkend=\"key_bindings\">Konfiguriraj bližnjice</link> "
"( <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving Around"
msgstr "Premikanje"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By Moving Around we mean the transfer of the keyboard and mouse focus "
"between the different parts of the &krusader; <link linkend=\"mainwindow"
"\">main window</link>. The focus can be in one of five places: the Left or "
"Right Panel, the Menu Bar, the Command Line or the Terminal Emulator. The "
"panel that has the focus is called the Active Panel. An Active Panel will "
"remain active until the other panel receives the focus (&ie;: if the Left "
"Panel was active and you clicked on the Command Line - then the Left Panel "
"remains the Active Panel). You must deliberately change which panel is "
"active."
msgstr ""
"S premikanjem mislimo na prenos fokusa tipkovnice in miške med različnimi "
"deli &krusader; <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">glavno okno</link>. Fokus je "
"lahko na enem od petih mest: na levi ali desni plošči, v menijski vrstici, v "
"ukazni vrstici ali v terminalskem emulatorju. Plošča, ki ima fokus, se "
"imenuje aktivna plošča. Aktivna plošča bo ostala aktivna, dokler druga "
"plošča ne prejme fokusa (&ie;: če je bila leva plošča aktivna in ste "
"kliknili na ukazno vrstico - potem leva plošča ostane aktivna plošča). "
"Morate namerno spremeniti, katera plošča je aktivna."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to transfer the focus to a specific panel is to use the "
"mouse to click on that panel. But you should be aware of the following:"
msgstr ""
"Najpogostejši način prenosa fokusa na določeno ploščo je, da z miško "
"kliknete na to ploščo. Vendar se morate zavedati naslednjega:"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the Toolbar, the FN keys bar or the Status Bar does "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> change the focus."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na orodno vrstico, vrstico s tipkami FN ali vrstico stanja se fokus "
"<emphasis>ne</emphasis> spremeni."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pushing the <guibutton>Run in Terminal Mode</guibutton> button in the "
"Command Line will not transfer the focus, so you have to click inside the "
"Input Line."
msgstr ""
"Potisk gumba <guibutton>Run in Terminal Mode</guibutton>(Zaženi v "
"terminalskem načinu) v ukazni vrstici ne bo prenesel fokusa, zato morate "
"klikniti v vnosno vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose a menu, the Menu Bar will become focused. It remains focused "
"until you choose a command - the focus returns to the previous owner."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete meni, se izostri menijska vrstica. Ostane osredotočen, dokler ne "
"izberete ukaza - fokus se vrne na prejšnjega lastnika."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are, of course, ways to use the keyboard to change the focus:"
msgstr "Seveda obstajajo načini, kako s tipkovnico spremeniti fokus:"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &Tab; Key will switch panels, if one of the panels has the focus or "
"rotate between all the commands in a menu, if the Menu Bar is active."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek &Tab; Tipka bo preklapljala med ploščami, če ima ena od plošč fokus, "
"ali vrtela med vsemi ukazi v meniju, če je menijska vrstica aktivna."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Down;</keycombo> will take you from "
"the Active Panel to the Command Line or Terminal Emulator, and the <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Up;</keycombo> will take you back from the Command "
"Line to the Active Panel."
msgstr ""
"Tipka <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Down;</keycombo> vas popelje iz "
"aktivne plošče v ukazno vrstico ali terminalski emulator, <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Up;</keycombo> vas bo vrnil iz ukazne vrstice na aktivno "
"ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &Esc; Key will make the Menu Bar return the focus, if it has it, to the "
"previous Active Panel."
msgstr ""
"&Esc; S tipko menijska vrstica vrne fokus, če ga ima, na prejšnjo aktivno "
"ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you happen to be inside the Terminal Emulator, you can use the &Tab; Key, "
"or the mouse, to navigate to an Active Panel."
msgstr ""
"Če ste slučajno znotraj terminalskega emulatorja, lahko uporabite &Tab; "
"Tipko ali miško za navigacijo do aktivne plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>Underlined Letter</"
"keycap></keycombo> from the Menu Bar will open that menu (unless this key "
"combination is a <quote>Reserved Key</quote>, used by one of &krusader;'s "
"actions)."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>Podčrtana črka</"
"keycap></keycombo> v menijski vrstici bo odprla ta meni (razen če je ta "
"kombinacija tipk <quote>Rezervirana tipka</quote>, ki jo uporablja eno od "
"dejanj &krusader;)."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting"
msgstr "Izbiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; offers 4 <link linkend=\"selection_modes\">Selection Modes</"
"link>, to say nothing about the <link linkend=\"quickselect\">Quickselect "
"bar</link>, only &krusader;'s Selection Mode is explained here."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; ponuja 4 <link linkend=\"selection_modes\">načine izbire</link>, "
"da ne omenjam <link linkend=\"quickselect\">vrstice za hitro izbiro</link>, "
"tukaj je razložen samo način izbire &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting is a skill you need to master in order to get the most out of "
"&krusader;. Since the Tree Panel allows select only one folder at a time, "
"this paragraph mainly explains how to select files in the List Panel."
msgstr ""
"Izbiranje je veščina, ki jo morate obvladati, da kar najbolje izkoristite "
"&krusader;. Ker drevesna plošča omogoča izbiro samo ene mape naenkrat, ta "
"odstavek v glavnem pojasnjuje, kako izbrati datoteke na plošči seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving the cursor is easy. Left-clicking on a file or folder (referred to "
"herein as <quote>elements</quote> meaning files and folders) will select it. "
"Here are some useful pointers that will make &krusader; even easier to use "
"(assuming you are using &krusader;'s Mouse Selection Mode):"
msgstr ""
"Premikanje kazalca je preprosto. Z levim klikom na datoteko ali mapo (v "
"nadaljevanju imenovano <quote>elementi</quote>, kar pomeni datoteke in "
"mape), jo boste izbrali. Tukaj je nekaj uporabnih napotkov, ki bodo "
"&krusader; še lažji za uporabo (ob predpostavki, da uporabljate način izbire "
"miške &krusader;):"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &Space; and &Ins; keys will toggle the selection of the file under the "
"cursor without affecting the selection of other files/folders, the cursor "
"will go one position down."
msgstr ""
"&Space; in &Ins; tipke preklopijo izbiro datoteke pod kazalcem, ne da bi "
"vplivale na izbiro drugih datotek/map, kazalec se pomakne za eno mesto "
"navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Left Clicking</keycap> on a file will select, or unselect, all "
"previously selected files."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>Levi klik</keycap> na datoteko bo izbral ali preklical izbor vseh "
"predhodno izbranih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Left Clicking</keycap></keycombo> "
"will toggle the selection of the file under the cursor without affecting the "
"selection of other files/folders."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Levi klik</keycap></keycombo> "
"preklopi izbiro datoteke pod kazalcem, ne da bi vplival na izbiro drugih "
"datotek/map."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>Left Clicking</keycap></keycombo> "
"will select all the elements between the previous cursor location and the "
"new one."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>Levi klik</keycap></keycombo> bo "
"izbral vse elemente med prejšnjim mestom kazalca in novim."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Home;</keycombo> selects everything above "
"the cursor (and deselects everything below the cursor, if selected)."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Home;</keycombo> izbere vse nad kazalcem "
"(in prekliče izbor vsega pod kazalcem, če je izbrano)."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&End;</keycombo> selects everything below "
"the cursor (and unselects everything above the cursor, if selected)."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&End;</keycombo> izbere vse pod kazalcem "
"(in prekliče izbor vsega nad kazalcem, če je izbrano)."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <quote>..</quote> entry is not selectable."
msgstr "Vnosa <quote>..</quote> ni mogoče izbrati."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"edit-menu\">Edit menu</link> can offer more ways to "
"select your files."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"edit-menu\">Meni Uredi</link> lahko ponudi več načinov za "
"izbiro datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Executing Commands"
msgstr "Izvajanje ukazov"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is not a lot to say here, all you need to do is select some files (if "
"you do not, &krusader; will operate on the file(s) or folder(s) that have "
"the focus), choose a <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Command</link> from the "
"Menu Bar or use a Keyboard Shortcut (or the Right Click Menu) and the "
"selected Command executes. See also <link linkend=\"executing_files"
"\">Executing Files</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj ni veliko za povedati, vse kar morate storiti je, da izberete nekaj "
"datotek (če tega ne storite, bo &krusader; deloval na datotekah ali mapah, "
"ki so v fokusu), izberite <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Ukaz</link> iz "
"menijske vrstice ali uporabite bližnjico na tipkovnici (ali meni z desnim "
"klikom) in izbrani ukaz se izvede. Glejte tudi <link linkend="
"\"executing_files\">Izvajanje datotek</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick search"
msgstr "Hitro iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature will do a quick search for the file name in the Active List "
"Panel."
msgstr "Ta funkcija bo hitro poiskala ime datoteke na plošči Active List."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <keycap>foo</keycap>(one character) to do a quick search in the Active "
"List Panel for a file beginning with <quote>foo</quote>. A small quick "
"search dialog box will open below the Active List Panel. Type the first few "
"characters of the desired file name (more than one character allowed), the "
"cursor will jump to that filename (if it exists), &eg; type <quote>ab</"
"quote> to search for a file which begins with <quote>ab</quote>. The &Up;/"
"&Down; keys will jump to the next or previous match. &Esc; will close the "
"quick search line. The cursor will stay on the last file found. The "
"Quicksearch supports <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Regular_expression\">regular expressions</ulink> for searching files."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <keycap>foo</keycap>(en znak) za hitro iskanje na plošči aktivnega "
"seznama za datoteko, ki se začne z <quote>foo</quote>. Pod ploščo aktivnega "
"seznama se bo odprlo majhno pogovorno okno za hitro iskanje. Vnesite prvih "
"nekaj znakov želenega imena datoteke (dovoljen je več kot en znak), kazalec "
"bo skočil na to ime datoteke (če obstaja), &eg; vnesite <quote>ab</quote>, "
"da poiščete datoteko, ki se začne z <quote>ab</quote>. Tipke &Up;/&Down; "
"bodo skočile na naslednjo ali prejšnjo tekmo. &Esc; zapre vrstico za hitro "
"iskanje. Kazalec bo ostal na zadnji najdeni datoteki. Quicksearch podpira "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regular_expression\">regularne "
"izraze</ulink> za iskanje datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>foo</keycap></"
"keycombo>, the key binding shortcut will be executed. If there is no "
"configured key binding, the remaining letter <keycap>foo</keycap> will be "
"used for the quick search."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>foo</keycap></"
"keycombo>, se bo izvršila bližnjica za vezavo tipk. Če ni nastavljene vezave "
"tipk, bo za hitro iskanje uporabljena preostala črka <keycap>foo</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite okno <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Konfiguriraj bližnjice</link> "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick filter"
msgstr "Hitri filter"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature will do a quick filter for the file list in the Active Panel."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija bo naredila hitri filter za seznam datotek na aktivni plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> to open Quickfilter bar. "
"Type <keycap>foo</keycap> (one character) to filter out from the Active "
"Panel all the files that do not have <quote>foo</quote> in names. You can "
"use wildcards for the filtering. &eg; use <quote>a*b</quote> to filter files "
"which have <quote>a</quote> and <quote>b</quote> in their names. The "
"Quickfilter follows the <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general\">case-"
"sensitivity setting</link> of Quicksearch."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo>, da odprete vrstico "
"hitrega filtra. Vnesite <keycap>foo</keycap> (en znak), da iz aktivne plošče "
"filtrirate vse datoteke, ki nimajo <quote>foo</quote> v imenu. Za "
"filtriranje lahko uporabite nadomestne znake. &eg; uporabite <quote>a*b</"
"quote> za filtriranje datotek, ki imajo v imenih <quote>a</quote> in "
"<quote>b</quote>. Quickfilter sledi <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general"
"\">nastavitvi občutljivosti na velike in male črke</link> hitrega iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing &Enter; in Quickfilter mode sets focus to panel, when panel or "
"Quickfilter is focused, &Esc; closes Quickfilter."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom &Enter; v načinu hitrega filtra nastavi fokus na ploščo, ko je "
"plošča ali hitri filter fokusiran, &Esc; zapre Quickfilter."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the default shortcut of Quickfilter use <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti privzeto bližnjico hitrega filtra, uporabite okno <link "
"linkend=\"key_bindings\">Konfiguracija bližnjic</link> "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguracija "
"bližnjic...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick select"
msgstr "Hitra izbira"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature will do a quick select for the file list in the Active Panel."
msgstr "Ta funkcija bo hitro izbrala seznam datotek na aktivni plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> to open "
"Quickselect bar. Type <keycap>foo</keycap> (one character) to filter out "
"from the Active Panel all the files that do not have <quote>foo</quote> in "
"names. You can use wildcards for the filtering. &eg; use <quote>a*b</quote> "
"to filter files which have <quote>a</quote> and <quote>b</quote> in their "
"names. The Quickselect follows the <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general"
"\">case-sensitivity setting</link> of Quicksearch."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>, da odprete "
"vrstico za hitro izbiro. Vnesite <keycap>foo</keycap> (en znak), da iz "
"aktivne plošče filtrirate vse datoteke, ki nimajo <quote>foo</quote> v "
"imenu. Za filtriranje lahko uporabite nadomestne znake. &eg; uporabite "
"<quote>a*b</quote> za filtriranje datotek, ki imajo v imenih <quote>a</"
"quote> in <quote>b</quote>. Quickselect sledi <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-"
"general\">nastavitvi občutljivosti na velike in male črke</link> Quicksearch."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing &Enter; in Quickselect mode sets focus to panel, when panel or "
"Quickselect is focused, &Esc; closes Quickselect."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom &Enter; v načinu Quickselect nastavi fokus na ploščo, ko je "
"plošča ali Quickselect fokusirana, &Esc; zapre Quickselect."

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the default shortcut of Quickselect use <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti privzeto bližnjico za Quickselect, uporabite okno <link "
"linkend=\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: title
#: basic-functions.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context Menu"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: basic-functions.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; has many Context menus that allow you to do fast operations with "
"the mouse, usually a right-click will open the Context menu (depending on "
"your <link linkend=\"selection_modes\">Selection Modes</link> settings). "
"This list gives an overview of the most important context menus. Use them to "
"discover the available commands."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; ima veliko kontekstnih menijev, ki vam omogočajo hitre operacije "
"z miško; običajno desni klik odpre kontekstni meni (odvisno od vaših "
"nastavitev <link linkend=\"selection_modes\">Izbirni načini</link>). Ta "
"seznam ponuja pregled najpomembnejših kontekstnih menijev. Z njimi odkrijte "
"razpoložljive ukaze."

